<td style="text-align:left">Query string to use with the initial connection to the server.  In server code, this can be accessed via <code>req.socket.handshake.query</code> in controller actions or <code>socket.handshake.query</code> in <a href="/documentation/reference/configuration/sails-config-sockets">socket lifecycle callbacks</a>.  Note that information about the sails.io.js SDK version will be tacked onto whatever query string you specify.</td>
